This script is intended to be used to quikly create a Certificate Authority (CA) for developing and/or testing porpuses.

The script mainly follows the steps by Jamie Nguyen in its page (https://jamielinux.com/docs/openssl-certificate-authority/index.html) with minor changes in directory structure.

There are three commands